cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "gsea-explorer: stateful exploratory analysis agent for GSEA enrichment results"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
type: software
authors:
  - alias: DDL095
repository-code: "https://github.com/DDL095/gsea-explorer"
url: "https://github.com/DDL095/gsea-explorer"
abstract: >-
  gsea-explorer is a stateful, question-driven exploratory analysis framework
  for GSEA enrichment results. It reads GSEA Capsule RDS (gsealens) or generic
  outputs (fgsea / clusterProfiler / enrichit), asks the user for experimental
  context at decision points, orchestrates cross-skill evidence gathering, and
  produces auditable Markdown reports using a GSEAlens-style |NES| enrichment
  direction framework. Supports multi-tissue crosstalk analysis and parallel
  deep-dive discussion across biological themes.
keywords:
  - GSEA
  - gene-set-enrichment-analysis
  - MSigDB
  - bioinformatics
  - transcriptomics
  - rstats
  - llm-agent
license: MIT
version: "0.5.5"
date-released: "2026-06-16"
